4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-strong_4-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-strong_4-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-strong_4-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-strong_4-3\"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Strong, S. M. (1946). Review of <i>Black Metropolis</i>. <i>American Sociological Review</i>, 11(2), 240\u2013241.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Peretz-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-Peretz_5-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-Peretz_5-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Peretz, H. (2004). \"The Making of <i>Black Metropolis</i>\", <i>The Annals of the American Academy of Political and Social Science</i>, 595, 168\u2013175.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.worldcat.org/title/black-metropolis-a-study-of-negro-life-in-a-northern-city/oclc/186494767/editions?referer=di&amp;editionsView=true\">\"Formats and Editions of <i>Black metropolis&#160;: a study of Negro life in a northern city</i> &#91;WorldCat.org&#93;\"</a>. <i>worldcat.org</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">February 15,</span> 2016</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=worldcat.org&amp;rft.atitle=Formats+and+Editions+of+Black+metropolis+%3A+a+study+of+Negro+life+in+a+northern+city+%5BWorldCat.org%5D&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldcat.org%2Ftitle%2Fblack-metropolis-a-study-of-negro-life-in-a-northern-city%2Foclc%2F186494767%2Feditions%3Freferer%3Ddi%26editionsView%3Dtrue&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABlack+Metropolis\" class=\"Z3988\"><spa